                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1355" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH BRASLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the child's mother. I was sweeping my room, and heard my little girl call out—I fetched her in—the prisoner ran</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183906170259"></xptr>
               <p>down stairs in about five minutes, and was in great distress about it—she said she had thrown the water out, and appeared very sorry.</p>
